# Import Direction Rule

의존 방향은 **항상 아래와 같다.**

```text
UI
↓
API
↓
Service
↓
Domain
```

## 허용

- UI → API, Service, Domain (필요 시)
- API → Service, Domain
- Service → Domain

## 금지

- domain → lib
- domain → api
- domain → ui
- lib → ui

*참조: `docs/architecture/DOMAIN_LAYER_TARGET_MAP.md`*
